00:19:00.416 --> 00:19:02.326 A:middle
I, also, encourage you to check

00:19:02.326 --> 00:19:04.886 A:middle
the app down here, where you can

00:19:04.946 --> 00:19:06.606 A:middle
select different screen sizes.

00:19:07.536 --> 00:19:08.756 A:middle
