00:19:19.476 --> 00:19:20.466 A:middle
adapt for right to left

00:19:20.466 --> 00:19:21.646 A:middle
languages, like Arabic or

00:19:21.716 --> 00:19:22.106 A:middle
Hebrew.

00:19:22.956 --> 00:19:24.846 A:middle
As I said earlier, we don't have

00:19:24.846 --> 00:19:26.046 A:middle
localizations for those

00:19:26.046 --> 00:19:26.706 A:middle
languages yet.

00:19:27.626 --> 00:19:28.756 A:middle
We can run another

00:19:28.756 --> 00:19:29.546 A:middle
pseudolanguage.

00:19:30.466 --> 00:19:31.796 A:middle
Let's open the Scheme Editor,

00:19:31.796 --> 00:19:34.366 A:middle
again, this time in application

00:19:34.426 --> 00:19:34.866 A:middle
language.

00:19:35.656 --> 00:19:36.516 A:middle
And I'm going to select the

00:19:36.516 --> 00:19:38.546 A:middle
Right to Left Pseudolanguage and

00:19:39.296 --> 00:19:41.266 A:middle
run the app in the simulator.

00:19:48.586 --> 00:19:49.016 A:middle
Okay.

00:19:49.166 --> 00:19:49.546 A:middle
Browse.

00:19:50.986 --> 00:19:53.166 A:middle
As you can here, our table will,

00:19:53.166 --> 00:19:55.316 A:middle
now flows from right to left

00:19:56.366 --> 00:19:57.806 A:middle
without us making any changes.

